messages.message:
Hey teamm, running into a couple issues on my sandbox (https://instabase.sandboxes.site/sandboxes/paulinecomising?cw=dev) that haven't resolved after pulling master, resyncing sandbox, and following threads for similar issues:
• this issue (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C05L87V014J/p1751461468685639) where my `trial has ended` but `Subscription & Billing` doesn't allow for commercial usage is still on my sandbox after pulling master to include Victor's PR
• when booting up weaviate-titan, I'm getting `unexpected status from POST request to https://549230430157.dkr.ecr.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/v2/instabase-build/weaviate-titan/blobs/uploads/: 404 Not Found` even after running `/home/owner/instabase/.sandbox/ibdev-backend/scripts/ecr-login` and restarting a few times
    ◦ I've tried clearing docker vars as noted here (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C05L87V014J/p1738150311357189?thread_ts=1738143000.926919&cid=C05L87V014J) and this also doesn't resolve it
Any tips on other things to try here?
